{"id": "1496540058252087316", "channel_id": "1496540058252087316", "author_id": "397832530965037057", "author_name": "matteo2011", "content": "As a new player, i have noticed a few things that could be improved:\n\n1. In the chapter and stage details page there should also be directly show the achievements. when you want to go back and achievement hunt, it is annoying and unnecessary having to click on the achievement and scroll to look for what you missed. instead just show the achievements next to the rating in the chapter. Lastly i see no reason to just also show the hidden silver completion in the chapter map too", "timestamp": "2026-04-22T15:55:54.257000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496540058252087316", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-22T18:38:47.322000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "👆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 7}], "attachments": [{"id": "1496540058470187008", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 765040, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496540058252087316/1496540058470187008/image.png?ex=69ea410a&is=69e8ef8a&hm=3ad1960c6257673a4b0eb5e42dd8dc5eb3f1d4431669ca104fc659b9781c7385&"}, {"id": "1496540058961055824", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-04-22_165513.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1133149, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496540058252087316/1496540058961055824/Screenshot_2026-04-22_165513.png?ex=69ea410a&is=69e8ef8a&hm=080a166ed835a3373f88528c68753612030d4fde690f0813029e6cf6e05ead33&"}]}
{"id": "1496540363723247768", "channel_id": "1496540058252087316", "author_id": "397832530965037057", "author_name": "matteo2011", "content": "2. Auto battle toggle available in map exploration rather than it only appearing once you are already in battle. The main reason this is useful may not be what you think, so currently you can only toggle auto during a battle and your choice for the auto will persist between fights, makes sense but this causes 1 problem, if you want to turn auto off for a elite/boss fight you can't until it makes at least 1 move for you. why would that be a problem? it is mostly a mild inconvenience, but there is a really bad possibility, imagine you need to do a achievement like \"draw X card\" but you didn't turn off auto before the boss, you got a awakener that has a exalt that can insta kills the boss. Guess what, auto does prioritize exalts and there is nothing that you can do to stop that from happening, so if you want that achievement you'll need to restart the whole investigation just because you couldn't turn off auto", "timestamp": "2026-04-22T15:57:07.087000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496540058252087316", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-22T15:58:00.377000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1496540363438031021", "filename": "Screenshot_2026-04-22_170300.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 945250, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496540058252087316/1496540363438031021/Screenshot_2026-04-22_170300.png?ex=69ea4153&is=69e8efd3&hm=a650997f870d15f6faa4b792d2ec7f19c4465265317ffd00a4b30092a27c3f4d&"}]}
{"id": "1496540415912841337", "channel_id": "1496540058252087316", "author_id": "397832530965037057", "author_name": "matteo2011", "content": "3. When losing a fight, merge the \"revive now\" and \"investigation failed\" window. This is mostly a matter of clarity, currently when you lose, the \"revive now\" window pops out first and if you refuse then the \"investigation failed\" window follows, with the option to either retry or retreat. I found it unclear, since there were times when i lost but knew that i could have won if i played differently, but the revive window pops up first and i though (especially early on) that if i refuse, the investigation would instantly end so even thought i wanted to save the gnosis i still used it because of a misunderstanding", "timestamp": "2026-04-22T15:57:19.530000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496540058252087316", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-22T16:07:59.678000+00:00", "reactions": [{"emoji": "🔥", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}]}
