{"id": "1496523374858338415", "channel_id": "1496523374858338415", "author_id": "1344504250784551014", "author_name": "syruponstrawberrycake", "content": "Edit: This interaction is intended as Light has written but I'll keep it up anyway because the thread was already made.\n\nThis is regarding Arachne pursuit and Ultra RM.\n\n> Ultra Mastery: For each 1 point of Realm Mastery, Singularity Beacon stacks from Singularity Prism and Dimension Shuttle increase by 0.05%.\n\n> Infinite Threads: Gain 10 stacks of Singularity Prism, deal [number] Final Verdict to the enemy with lowest HP.\n(Note this is with e3 Arachne which I have)\n\nArachne's pursuit Infinite Threads gives 10 stacks of Singularity Prism, but the Beacon stacks seem to not get affected by Ultra Mastery and I am wondering if this is intended.\n\nThis is an example with Pure Ultra 327 RM which RM gives 32% more Beacon stacks but Pursuit still gives 10 stacks of Beacon despite the Prism --> Beacon conversion buff.", "timestamp": "2026-04-22T14:49:36.626000+00:00", "thread_id": "1496523374858338415", "edited_timestamp": "2026-04-22T15:30:46.302000+00:00", "attachments": [{"id": "1496523375626158263", "filename": "2ktf39h.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1935287, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1496523374858338415/1496523375626158263/2ktf39h.png?ex=69ea3180&is=69e8e000&hm=f0a896a8f2bccbcf8b1945acb31da9ea297cd1773be7ad9520597b411d85b7da&"}]}
